==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prolongable
<hw>Pro*long"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of
being prolonged; <as>as, life is <ex>prolongable</ex> by
care</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Each syllable being a <qex>prolongable</qex> quantity.</q>
<rj><qau>Rush.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prolongate</ent>⟦br⟧
